  <description type="morphology">Subshrubs, spreading, densely branched, (0.5–)1–8 × 2–8 dm. Leaf blades linear-lanceolate to elliptic or spatulate, 0.4–1.2(–1.5) × 0.2–0.8 cm, thinly tomentose abaxially. Inflorescences 1–5(–8) × 3–10 cm; branches diffuse, with dichotomously arranged involucres, slender, sharply ridged and deeply grooved, minutely scabrellous, not spinose. Involucres campanulate, 0.7–1.5(–2) × 0.7–1.5(–2) mm. Flowers 1.5–2.5 mm; perianth yellowish white.</description>
